jqBdNsERE</b>

356
00:23:31.390 --> 00:23:36.230
Having a bunch of lowlife retainers
like you would only disgrace Oden!

357
00:23:36.230 --> 00:23:40.940
Lord Oden, would you kindly elaborate
on your temperament this fine morning?

358
00:23:40.940 --> 00:23:43.690
This ganmodoki is exquisite!

359
00:23:45.070 --> 00:23:48.110
What is the matter with you all?!
You are all creeping me out!

360
00:23:48.110 --> 00:23:52.080
He is the man who will one day
become the shogun of Wano!

361
00:23:52.410 --> 00:23:56.960
Those who serve him ought to be
the best samurai Wano has to offer!

362
00:24:21.190 --> 00:24:24.280
Of course, protecting your lord is a must.

363
00:24:24.280 --> 00:24:26.320
The capital city...

364
00:24:26.320 --> 00:24:31.830
No, the entire country of Wano
will have you as its guardians!

365
00:24:34.790 --> 00:24:38.670
<b>Three Years Later



Thirty Years Before

the Present Day</b>

366
00:24:38.670 --> 00:24:47.630
<b>Flower

Capital</b>

367
00:24:38.670 --> 00:24:42.420
I hear the daimyo of Kuri
and his court are coming to the capital.

368
00:24:43.040 --> 00:24:44.920
Make sure you don't get robbed.

369
00:24:44.920 --> 00:24:47.630
Lord Oden's retainers are known thugs.

370
00:24:47.630 --> 00:24:50.010
Look! They're here!

371
00:24:50.010 --> 00:24:50.970
– Wha...?
– Huh?

372
00:24:51.390 --> 00:24:52.050
What?!

373
00:25:21.170 --> 00:25:23.670
Oh, my! Look at those samurai!

374
00:25:23.670 --> 00:25:26.590
Were Lord Oden's retainers
always so dignified?

375
00:25:27.010 --> 00:25:28.470
I hardly recognized them!

376
00:25:28.470 --> 00:25:30.550
It's like a shogun's procession!

377
00:25:39.350 --> 00:25:46.440
The regal postures of those samurai were
so glorious that some people even forgot to breathe.

378
00:25:46.440 --> 00:25:52.950
And one could have seen people drop
to their knees everywhere in the capital.

379
00:25:56.450 --> 00:25:58.700
Hey, Father!

380
00:25:58.700 --> 00:25:59.750
Oden!

381
00:25:59.750 --> 00:26:01.620
You have become such a fine man!

382
00:26:01.620 --> 00:26:03.290
Everyone is surprised!

383
00:26:03.290 --> 00:26:05.590
I have only been made into a fine man.

384
00:26:05.590 --> 00:26:07.920
But I am still the same as ever!

385
00:26:08.710 --> 00:26:11.880
M-M-My Oden feels grateful toward others?!

386
00:26:12.260 --> 00:26:14.180
Why should that scare you?

387
00:26:20.890 --> 00:26:26.480
Hearing of his father's illness, Oden rushed to the capital
and was relieved to see him in good health.

388
00:26:26.480 --> 00:26:31.150
However, this would be the last time
they ever exchanged words.

389
00:26:35.570 --> 00:26:37.660
It seems this place is inhabited.

390
00:26:38.080 --> 00:26:41.370
Pops, it'll take a week to repair it.

391
00:26:41.750 --> 00:26:44.040
The water damaged most of the cargo!

392
00:26:44.040 --> 00:26:48.670
<b>The Same Year...


Itachi Port

Kuri</b>

393
00:26:44.420 --> 00:26:47.000
We need to procure supplies.

394
00:26:47.000 --> 00:26:48.670
Who wants to go?!

395
00:26:48.670 --> 00:26:52.260
Almost everyone since we all
need some exercise.

396
00:26:56.680 --> 00:27:00.310
<b>Captain Edward Newgate


Whitebeard Pirates</b>

397
00:26:57.390 --> 00:26:59.850
We climbed up the falls, right?

398
00:27:03.520 --> 00:27:06.980
Why is there sea and an island here?

399
00:27:13.030 --> 00:27:15.490
We have a problem, Sir Kanjuro!

400
00:27:16.780 --> 00:27:17.620
What is it?

401
00:27:17.620 --> 00:27:20.240
Calm yourself! You are too loud!

402
00:27:20.240 --> 00:27:24.120
We received a report that
a pirate ship docked at Itachi Port!

403
00:27:24.120 --> 00:27:25.330
Pirates?!

404
00:27:30.090 --> 00:27:31.420
Lord Oden!

405
00:27:31.420 --> 00:27:33.260
Where are you going?!

406
00:27:33.260 --> 00:27:35.090
To the port!

407
00:27:36.590 --> 00:27:39.100
Here I go! Here I go!

408
00:27:40.510 --> 00:27:43.180
Alright, we'll go fetch some supplies.

409
00:27:43.180 --> 00:27:45.100
I'm coming, too!

410
00:27:45.100 --> 00:27:46.100
You can't.

411
00:27:46.100 --> 00:27:47.980
You're just an apprentice!

412
00:27:47.980 --> 00:27:49.560
Don't say that!

413
00:27:49.560 --> 00:27:52.360
Pops! Can I go?

414
00:27:52.360 --> 00:27:53.990
Do as you like.

415
00:27:54.780 --> 00:27:57.860
All right! Let's go!

416
00:27:55.450 --> 00:27:57.860
Hurry up! Hurry up!

417
00:27:57.860 --> 00:27:59.990
I said no apprentices allowed!

418
00:27:59.990 --> 00:28:00.990
Stay here!

419
00:28:01.370 --> 00:28:02.490
What?!

420
00:28:02.490 --> 00:28:04.790
Lord Oden went to the port?!

421
00:28:05.870 --> 00:28:07.540
Why did you let him go?!

422
00:28:07.540 --> 00:28:09.830
I heard there's a pirate ship at Itachi Port!

423
00:28:09.830 --> 00:28:11.210
It's unusual, too!

424
00:28:11.210 --> 00:28:13.500
They say it's big and the pirates look tough!

425
00:28:14.130 --> 00:28:15.550
We must stop him!

426
00:28:15.550 --> 00:28:18.130
He just went to chase them away, right?!

427
00:28:18.130 --> 00:28:19.390
Not likely!

428
00:28:19.390 --> 00:28:21.010
I am sure you know about...

429
00:28:21.680 --> 00:28:23.350
Lord Oden's dream!

430
00:28:27.850 --> 00:28:31.020
Is that a pirate ship?!

431
00:28:31.020 --> 00:28:33.020
I have been waiting...

432
00:28:33.780 --> 00:28:36.190
for this moment!

433
00:28:37.990 --> 00:28:39.360
Here comes trouble.

434
00:28:41.070 --> 00:28:43.080
Hey, all of you! Stand back!

435
00:28:43.080 --> 00:28:43.870
– What?
– What?

436
00:28:44.410 --> 00:28:46.540
Something's coming!

437
00:28:46.540 --> 00:28:48.620
Something unthinkable!

438
00:28:48.620 --> 00:28:50.210
Well done!

439
00:28:50.540 --> 00:28:55.880
You made it past the terrible weather
and waterfalls! Quite impressive!

440
00:29:11.100 --> 00:29:16.190
I have been waiting for you, pirates!

441
00:29:34.040 --> 00:29:36.460
You are really something else!

442
00:29:37.130 --> 00:29:38.630
I'll make you pay for that!

443
00:29:40.840 --> 00:29:43.760
Bring it on, you punk!

444
00:30:12.960 --> 00:30:16.000
I have been waiting for someone like you!

445
00:30:16.500 --> 00:30:19.090
My name is Kozuki Oden!

446
00:30:19.090 --> 00:30:21.760
I do not know who you are,
but please allow me...

447
00:30:22.180 --> 00:30:23.630
to ride on your ship!
